    "For example, sketch share both a raster and a vector representation, thus inspiring researchers to take different generative approaches [30,82,144,146,147].Next, we summarize typical tasks in Diffusion-Based Visual Art Creation:• Quality Enhancement.",
    "As the baseline task in content generation and the basic requirement in visual art creation, the generated content should possess higher resolution and better quality.",
    "This is commonly realized by aesthetic training data, advanced model structure, more parameters, and result optimization designs.",
    "In the post-diffusion era, these methods are integrated into training foundation models [22,54,108,118,176].• Controllable Generation.",
    "The requirement emerges from artists' need to precisely control each perspective of their generated results, including context, subject, content, and style."
  ]
